   125 + {                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
   126 +        /*                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
   127 +         * poll is used for asynchronous I/O multiplexing (select/poll/epoll).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
   128 +         * It allows a user program to wait for multiple devices to become                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
   129 +         * ready for reading or writing without blocking on each one.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
